# Query Playbook

Use this playbook to translate messy user language into useful workflow-search
queries.

## Normalize The Ask

Extract these fields before searching:

| Field | Meaning |
| --- | --- |
| Domain | healthcare, education, real estate, public evidence, legal, finance, geospatial, etc. |
| Input | files, addresses, records, links, forms, tickets, photos, source lists, patient packets, listings, permits |
| Output artifact | evidence packet, completed document, checklist, report, queue item, case note, decision memo |
| Workflow pattern | evidence audit, document transformation, case intake, compliance support, queue processing, monitoring, human review |
| Safety boundary | what the agent must not decide or claim |
| Source type | public web, official records, internal files, APIs, databases, human-provided documents |
| Human review | whether a person must approve, submit, certify, publish, or decide |

When the user gives a vague phrase, infer these fields from examples and then
state the inference briefly.

## Workflow Pattern Map

| User language | Pattern labels | Search angle |
| --- | --- | --- |
| "like my earthquake thing" | EvidenceAudit, PublicRecordsInvestigation, ComplianceBoundary, HumanReview, SourceAtlas | public evidence audit, OSINT, due diligence, hazard/geospatial evidence |
| "patient data to documents" | DocumentTransformation, CaseIntake, HumanReview, ComplianceBoundary | healthcare document processing, referral packet, prior authorization, intake |
| "education workflow" | EducationSupport, Assessment, TutorOps, CurriculumOps, CaseIntake | education agent workflow, tutoring agent, assessment workflow, student support |
| "real estate workflow" | DueDiligence, Underwriting, EvidenceAudit, DocumentAbstraction | CRE due diligence, lease abstraction, underwriting agent skills |
| "process many records" | WorkQueueOps, BatchOps, QueueReview | durable queue, batch workflow, checklist queue, review queue |
| "watch for changes" | Monitoring, EventDrivenOps, Escalation | monitoring agent, alert workflow, source watch, filing/news monitor |
| "human approves first" | HumanReview, ApprovalGate, SafeOutputs | human in the loop, approval workflow, review gate |
| "what repo teaches types" | PatternRouter, WorkflowCatalog, SkillRegistry | agent workflow patterns, skill catalog, workflow templates |

## Earthquake / Building Evidence Mapping

Map "earthquake thing" to:

- real-world public evidence audit;
- deterministic source collection before agent synthesis;
- bounded parallel source lanes for identity, official records, incidents/news,
  contractor/developer/professional traces, geospatial/hazard context, and review;
- validation gate for citation quality, source reachability, source limits, and
  overclaim prevention;
- manual-request handoff when official records are not publicly available;
- human review before any safety, compliance, legal, engineering, or occupancy
  conclusion.

Useful search phrases:

```text
public evidence audit agent skill
OSINT evidence workflow agent repo
building permit due diligence workflow agent
geospatial hazard evidence agent skill
compliance boundary human review agent workflow
real-world agent skill public records investigation
```

## Domain Query Seeds

Healthcare:

```text
agent skills healthcare intake workflow
healthcare referral packet agent workflow
prior authorization document workflow agent
medical document processing human review agent
healthcare admin agent skills
medical research skill library
```

Education:

```text
education agent workflow templates
student support agent skill
curriculum planning agent workflow
assessment feedback agent workflow
research assistant education skill
```

Real estate:

```text
real estate due diligence agent skill
commercial real estate underwriting agent workflow
lease abstraction agent skill
property permit public records workflow agent
real estate closing checklist agent
```

Multi-industry catalogs:

```text
multi industry AI agent workflow catalog
agent skills healthcare real estate education
AI agent templates healthcare education real estate
Codex compatible agent skills catalog
SKILL.md workflow packs industry
```

## Ranking Heuristic

Score candidates higher when they have:

- reusable skill/workflow package files;
- explicit industry or workflow categories;
- examples across healthcare, education, real estate, public evidence, legal, or
  finance;
- schemas, validators, reports, evidence logs, or human-review gates;
- Codex/Claude/OpenClaw/OpenAI skill compatibility;
- active maintenance or substantial community signal;
- clear safety boundaries for regulated or high-consequence domains.

Score lower when they are only a model demo, a generic chatbot, an app platform
with no reusable workflow taxonomy, or a code-only agent workflow.


